data.description: BRAND NEW PAINT AND CARPET IN ENTIRE HOUSE. VA ASSUMABLE LOAN AT 3.25%. This three-bedroom, two-bath abode, with its two-car garage, is a perfect concept or a home. The open floor plan, characterized by unobstructed transitions and a cohesive design narrative, enhances the dwelling's aesthetic and functional appeal. Each room, meticulously crafted, resonates with a distinct identity, yet seamlessly integrates into the overall design ethos, making the house a harmonious amalgamation of elegance and contemporary living. The residence, with its architectural finesse and meticulous attention to detail, stands perfectly in the center of Edmonds growing entertainment districts, blocks from new dining options, golf, Homeland Grocery, Portland ave and the turnpike! Seller is willing to offer a rate buy down with an acceptable offer.
